					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In the object system of one of my NES games, each object has a &quot;state&quot; and a &quot;state timer&quot;. The state timer can be programmed to subtract 1 every frame, or every tenth of a second (6 frames on NTSC or 5 on PAL), or whatever.</div>

