					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You basically want a JSR (vector). The above does that. First it does the JSR part, then it uses JMP (vector) to do the (vector) part of the JSR. Now it's at the routine like you want, and an RTS returns to just after the JSR like you want.</div>

